headline: Northern Trust Appointed as Asset Servicing Provider by Australian Insurer Generation Life
summary: MELBOURNE, Australia, February 25, 2025--Northern Trust will provide global custody and valuation reporting to AU$1.5 billion (as of 31 January 2025) of Generation Life’s portfolio assets.
